  "notes": "DSPT-ONT provides a comprehensive model of the NHS Data Security and Protection Toolkit enabling AI-agent-driven compliance assessment for health sector organisations. Includes pre-built cross-framework mappings linking DSPT standards to NCSC CAF contributing outcomes (19 mappings), enabling organisations to demonstrate compliance across both frameworks simultaneously. Bridges to GDPR for data protection alignment and GRC-FW for organisational compliance posture tracking."
